      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEAUTIFUL CHILD (1) was well fancied last time and led throughout to score (34.27) at this track in a Grade 5 over 600m. Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with two wins from two starts. Sure to prove hard to beat. GORDON KEEPING (2) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 3rd on July 5 over 600m at this track behind BEAUTIFUL CHILD beaten 6 lengths (34.71) in a Grade 5. Likely to be in the finish again. UNDER ANESTHETIC (3) is a super honest type rarely out of the placings, including wins at his last two on end, the latest at The Gardens (29.74). Strike rate this course strong having won two of four tries. Expected to feature on best form. COOLHAND SUE (4) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
